.Sh NAME
.Nm dl-applefonts
.Nd download and install Apple fonts
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.\" For a program:  program [-abc] file ...
.Nm dl-applefonts
.Op Fl o Ar outdir
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility downloads and installs Apple fonts to the
.Em /fonts
subdirectory of
.Ev $XDG_DATA_HOME ,
or 
.Ar outdir
if 
.Fl o
is used.
